      "transition_readiness_know_how_take_medicines_without_help_comments": "I know how to take my medicines (time, dosage, and frequency) without help. Comments:",
      "transition_readiness_aware_hydroxyurea_how_affects_sickle_cell_disease": "I am aware of what hydroxyurea is and how it affects sickle cell disease. (If you are not taking this medicine please check: Not Applicable)",
      "transition_readiness_aware_hydroxyurea_how_affects_sickle_cell_disease_opt_1": "Strongly Agree",
      "transition_readiness_aware_hydroxyurea_how_affects_sickle_cell_disease_opt_2": "Somewhat Agree",
      "transition_readiness_aware_hydroxyurea_how_affects_sickle_cell_disease_opt_3": "Neither Agree nor Disagree",
