      "transition_readiness_aware_hydroxyurea_how_affects_sickle_cell_disease_comments": "I am aware of what hydroxyurea is and how it affects sickle cell disease. (If you are not taking this medicine please check: Not Applicable) Comments:",
      "transition_readiness_understan_drugs_alcohol_tobacco_usage_affect_sickle_cell_disease": "I understand how drugs, alcohol, and tobacco usage affect sickle cell disease.",
      "transition_readiness_understan_drugs_alcohol_tobacco_usage_affect_sickle_cell_disease_opt_1": "Strongly Agree",
