      "transition_readiness_understan_drugs_alcohol_tobacco_usage_affect_sickle_cell_disease_comments": "I understand how drugs, alcohol, and tobacco usage affect sickle cell disease. Comments:",
      "education_section_description": "Are you ready for your future? Do you have a 504 plan or IEP? Take a few minutes to identify your areas of strength and highlight where there is room to grow!",
